---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<BaseLayout title="页面未找到 | Tim Chen" description="这个页面不存在。">
  <main id="content" class="shell page-simple">
    <section class="section">
      <div class="section-head">
        <p class="eyebrow" data-i18n="notfound_eyebrow">404</p>
        <h1 class="section-title" data-i18n="notfound_title">这个页面走丢了</h1>
        <p class="section-desc" data-i18n="notfound_desc">旧路径已经下线，当前站点正在按新设计持续重建中。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="actions">
        <a class="button button-primary" href="/" data-i18n="notfound_btn_home">回首页</a>
        <a class="button button-secondary" href="/about/" data-i18n="notfound_btn_about">看关于</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="contact-card">
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow" data-i18n="notfound_hint_eyebrow">Hint</p>
          <h2 class="section-title" data-i18n="notfound_hint_title">从这两个入口继续</h2>
          <p class="section-desc" data-i18n="notfound_hint_desc">首页看最新模块，关于页看个人方向与能力结构。</p>
        </div>
        <aside class="contact-note">
          <p><strong data-i18n="notfound_tip_title">Tip</strong></p>
          <p data-i18n="notfound_tip_desc">如果你是从旧收藏夹进来的，建议更新到新链接。</p>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
